{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01AaczGg8cAz2GTJJZUL13Fz","type":"tool_result","content":"# Harness Cost Report\n\nTotal API-equivalent cost: $789.48\nTotal API calls: 5765\nAverage cost per story: $3.73 (158 stories)\n\n## Cost by Token Type\n\n| Type | Tokens | Rate | Cost | % |\n|------|--------|------|------|---|\n| Cache reads | 310,416,568 | $1.50/MTok | $465.62 | 59% |\n| Cache writes | 10,682,383 | $18.75/MTok | $200.29 | 25% |\n| Output | 1,644,607 | $75/MTok | $123.35 | 16% |\n| Input | 13,999 | $15/MTok | $0.21 | 0% |\n\n## Cost by Phase\n\n| Phase | Calls | Cost | % |\n|-------|-------|------|---|\n| verify | 3373 | $423.25 | 53.6% |\n| orchestrator | 795 | $172.25 | 21.8% |\n| retro | 651 | $89.57 | 11.3% |\n| code-review | 331 | $37.75 | 4.8% |\n| create-story | 344 | $36.58 | 4.6% |\n| dev-story | 271 | $30.07 | 3.8% |\n\n## Cost by Tool\n\n| Tool | Calls | Cost | % |\n|------|-------|------|---|\n| Bash | 2194 | $270.02 | 34.2% |\n| Read | 1195 | $163.00 | 20.6% |\n| Edit | 864 | $111.76 | 14.2% |\n| Agent | 540 | $70.84 | 9.0% |\n| Skill | 188 | $65.26 | 8.3% |\n| Grep | 382 | $43.96 | 5.6% |\n| Write | 153 | $27.32 | 3.5% |\n| Glob | 106 | $18.55 | 2.4% |\n| TodoWrite | 111 | $15.24 | 1.9% |\n| ToolSearch | 28 | $3.10 | 0.4% |\n\n## Top 10 Most Expensive Stories\n\n| Story | Calls | Cost | % |\n|-------|-------|------|---|\n| unknown | 1002 | $199.37 | 25.3% |\n| 16-5-rewrite-harness-run-verification-dispatch | 417 | $49.42 | 6.3% |\n| 1-1-foo | 198 | $24.35 | 3.1% |\n| 14-5-stack-aware-verify-dockerfile | 190 | $23.63 | 3.0% |\n| 14-4-observability-backend-choice | 192 | $22.13 | 2.8% |\n| 8-9-semgrep-rules-rust-observability | 121 | $17.10 | 2.2% |\n| 8-2-expand-state-types-for-rust | 84 | $12.67 | 1.6% |\n| 9-5-multi-stack-docs-remaining-consumers | 84 | $11.07 | 1.4% |\n| 11-2-sprint-status-yaml-derived-view | 74 | $10.80 | 1.4% |\n| 11-1-unified-sprintstate-schema-versioning | 75 | $10.27 | 1.3% |\n[OK]