nificant tokens.\n\nProduce a retrospective that covers:\n1. **Session summary** — no-op session fixing state corruption for the 68th time\n2. **Issues analysis** — the Ralph state corruption root cause, token waste\n3. **Cost analysis** — from the cost report, focus on waste from no-op sessions\n4. **What went well** — efficient fix (minimal tool calls)\n5. **What went wrong** — Ralph still not stopped, 68 sessions of waste\n6. **Lessons learned** — need circuit breaker or Ralph stop mechanism\n7. **Action items** — stop Ralph, investigate root cause of state reversion\n\nIf a session retro for today (2026-03-28) already exists, append to it with a `---` separator and timestamp.\n\nWrite the retrospective to _bmad-output/implementation-artifacts/session-retro-2026-03-28.md.\n\nDo NOT ask the user any questions — proceed autonomously.\nDo NOT run git commit. Do NOT run git add. Do NOT modify sprint-status.yaml.","agentId":"a9d1be1757f3ab2ee","agentType":"general-purpose","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Retrospective written to `/Users/ivintik/dev/personal/codeharness/_bmad-output/implementation-artifacts/session-retro-2026-03-28.md`.\n\nSummary:\n- **Session 86, no-op #68** appended to the existing retro file with `---` separator\n- **Total spend:** $789.48 across 5,765 API calls\n- **Estimated waste from no-op loop:** $250-290 (32-37% of total sprint budget)\n- **Cost acceleration:** ~$2.50/session burning on pure waste\n- **Root cause unchanged:** Ralph's stale in-memory state overwrites the 4 completed stories (16-5 through 16-8) every iteration\n- **The only fix:** Kill the Ralph process. The sprint is done. There is nothing left to build. This has been the recommendation for 68 consecutive sessions."}],"totalDurationMs":72277,"totalTokens":33744,"totalToolUseCount":10,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":2044,"cache_read_input_tokens":31488,"output_tokens":211,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier"